Fundamental Boolean model Example

Source: R/Common_Genes_Clusters.R
Common_Genes_Clusters.Rd

data(Common_Genes_Clusters)

Format

An object of class 'list';

References

Chen et al.(2018), Front. Physiol., 25 September 2018, (Front. Physiol.)
